title: This Scammy GoFundMe Campaign For A $20 Million Wedding Got Dragged To GTFOHville
text:
The Internet Vs. The $20 Million GoFundMe Wedding Dr. Erinn Michelle Haynes seems like a decent person who wouldn’t ask the internet to pay for her $20 MILLION WEDDING but that’s exactly what she did–BOLDLY–in a hilariously headassey moment that sparked hilarious chaos across Twitter.

Hit the flip for the funniest (and pettiest) reactions to the $20 million GoFundMe wedding campaign.
